# AI governance generated by `sdg-agents init`
# This repo is the generator: everything below is a mirror of src/assets/, so the
# source of truth is already versioned. E5 revisits which backlog files get
# committed here. The three explicit paths are what the CLI itself emits into a
# consumer's .gitignore; keeping them stops every dogfood run from re-appending.
.ai/
.ai/backlog/tasks.md
.ai/backlog/impact-map.md
.ai/last-prompt.md
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

